nichirakulla Moham]]'' (1989) .... Govindan\n#''[[V.I.P. (1989 film)|V.I.P.]] '' (1989).... Kuttoos\n#''[[Pattana Pravesham]]'' (1988)\n#''[[Kandathum Kettathum]]'' (1988).... Sadananthan\n#''[[Moonnam Mura]]'' (1988)\n#''[[Athirthikal]]'' (1988)\n#''[[Sankhanadam]]'' (1988)\n#''[[Janmatharam]]'' (1988).... Karunan\n#''[[Unnikrishnante Adyathe Christmas]]'' (1988)\n#''[[Onninu Purake Mattonnu]]'' (1988) .... Appu\n#''[[Loose Loose Arappiri Loose]]'' (1988)\n#''[[Janmandharam]]'' (1988)\n#''[[Ulsavapittennu]]'' (1988)\n#''[[Swargam]]'' (1987)\n#''[[Nirabhedangal]]'' (1987) .... Krishan\n#''[[Agnimuhurtham]]'' (1987)\n#''[[Oru Sindoora Pottinte Ormakku]]'' (1987)\n#''[[Ivare Sookshikkuka]]'' (1987)\n#''[[Mangalya Charthu]]'' (1987)...Pappan\n#''[[Kottum Kuravayum]]'' (1987)\n#''[[Athinumappuram]]'' (1987)\n#''[[Kalam Mari Katha Mari]]'' (1987) .... Koya\n#''[[Revathikkoru Pavakkutty]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Pappan Priyappetta Pappan]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Oppam Oppathinoppam]]'' (1986)....Neelakandan\n#''[[Kunjattakilikal]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Naale Njagalude Vivaham]]'' (1986).... Mathachan\n#''[[Ennu Nadhante Nimmi]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Nyayavidhi]]'' (1986).... Mathunni\n#''Ente Entethumathrem'' (1986)\n#''Manjamantharangal'' (1986)\n#''[[Kshamichu Ennoru Vakku]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Adukkan Entheluppam]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Geetham (film)|Geetham]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Shyama (film)|Shyama]]'' (1986)\n#''Alorugi Arangorugi'' (1986)\n#''Moonnu Masagalkku Munbu'' (1986)\n#''[[Prathyekam Sradhikkukka]]'' (1986) ...Detective Veerabhadran\n#''[[Atham Chithira Chothi]]'' (1986)..... Pushkaran\n#''[[Snehamulla Simham]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Veendum]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Padayani]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Icecream]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Rareeram]]'' (1986).... Aravindakshan\n#''[[Ponnumkudathinu Pottu]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Katturumbinum Kathukuthu]]'' (1986).... Johny\n#''[[Ithramathram (1986 film)|Ithramathram]]'' (1986) .... Augustine\n#''[[Oru Yugasandhya]]'' (1986).... Kuttappan\n#''[[Akalagalil]]'' (1986)\n# Love Story (1986)\n#''[[Ninnishtam Ennishtam]]'' (1986)\n#''[[Upahaaram]]'' (1985).... Sundareshan\n#''[[Vellarikka Pattanam]]'' (1985)\n#''[[Premalekhanam]]'' (1985)\n#''[[Koodum Thedi]]'' (1985) .... Vasu\n#''[[Akkare Ninnoru Maran]]'' (1985)\n#''[[Makan Ente Makan]]'' (1985)\n#''[[Oru Nokku Kanan]]'' (1985) .... Vidyadharan Mashu\n#''[[Kandu Kandarinju]]'' (1985) .... Kittan\n#''[[Maniyara]]'' (1985)\n#''[[Akkachide Kunjuvava]]'' (1985)\n#''[[Oru Kudakeezhil]]'' (1985) .... Pushpangathan\n#''[[Scene No 7]]'' (1985)\n#''[[Black Mail (1985 film)|Black Mail]]'' (1985)\n# ''[[Akalathe Ambili]]'' (1985)\n#''[[Shantham Bheekaram]]'' (1985)\n#''[[Shatru]]'' (1985) .... Thamarakshan/Kottada Vasu\n#''[[Thathamme Poocha Poocha]]'' (1984)\n#''[[Koottinilamkili]]'' (1984)\n#''[[Manithali]]'' (1984).... Subaid\n#''[[Vanitha Police]]'' (1984)\n#''[[Poochakkoru Mookkuthi]]'' (1984)\n#''[[Swantham Sarika]]'' (1984)\n#''[[Kaliyil Alpam Karyam]]'' (1984)\n#''[[Kadamattathachan (1984 film)|Kadamattathachan]]'' (1984).... Ithappiri\n#''[[NH 47 (film)|NH 47]]'' (1984)\n#''[[Pavam Krooran]]'' (1984).... Mathulan\n#''[[Velichamillatha Veethikal]]'' (1984)\n#''[[Ethirppukal]]'' (1984)\n#''[[Theere Pratheekshikkathe]]'' (1984)....Karunan\n#''[[Vepralam]]'' (1984)\n#''[[Sreekrishnaparundu]]'' (1984)\n#''[[Belt Mathai]]'' (1983)...Kuttan Pilla\n#''[[Aana (film)|Aana]]'' (1983).... Thomas\n#''[[Pourusham]]'' (1983)\n#''[[Mazhanilavu]]'' (1983) .... Mathukutty\n#''[[Ee Yugam]]'' (1983)\n#''[[Rathilayam]]'' (1983)....Lonappan\n#''[[Thavalam (1983 film)|Thavalam]]'' (1983)...Vaasu\n#''[[Maniyara]]'' (1983).... Moideenkutty\n#''[[Kolakomban]]'' (1983)\n#''[[Nizhal Moodiya Nirangal]]'' (1983).... Kuruppu\n#[[Coolie (Malayalam film)|Coolie]] (1983)\n#''[[Pooviriyum Pulari]]'' (1982)\n#''[[Kakka]]'' (1982)\n#''[[Mylanchi]]'' (1982) .... Moosa\n#''[[Ethiralikal]]'' (1982) .... Pareed\n#''[[Komaram]]'' (1982)\n#''[[Kolakomban]]'' (1982)\n#''[[Ariyappedatha Rahasyam]]'' (1981).... Gopi\n#''[[Aarathi]]'' (1981)\n#''[[Greeshmajwala]]'' (1981) .... Nair\n#''[[Swapnaraagam]]'' (1981)\n#''[[Sphodanam]]'' (1981) ...Vasu Pilla\n#''[[Vayal]]'' (1981)....Naanu Nair\n#''[[Arayannam]]'' (1981) .... Antony\n#''[[Sambavam]]'' (1981)\n#''[[Thadavara]]'' (1981) .... Karnan\n#''[[Raktham]]'' (1981)\n#''[[Tharavu]]'' (1981) .... Thanki\n#''[[Sphodanam]]'' (1981)\n#''[[Avatharam (1981 film)|Avatharam]]'' (1981) .... Parasahayam Thankappan\n#''[[Itha Oru Dhikkari]]'' (1981).... Kumar\n#''[[Thakilu Kottampuram]]'' (1981) ... Vasu\n#''[[Dhandha Yudham]]'' (1981)\n#''[[Oru Vilippadakale]]'' (1981)\n#''[[Daliyapookkal]]'' (1980)\n#''[[Kaavalmaadam]]'' (1980).....Rappai\n#''[[Adhikaram]]'' (1980) .... Appukuttan\n#''[[Deepam (film)|Deepam]]'' (1980) .... Subrahmanyam\n#''[[Arangum Aniyarayum]]'' (1980) .... Ananthan\n#''[[Chakara]]'' (1980) .... Kochu Pilla\n#''[[Thaliritta Kinakkal]]'' (1980)\n#''[[Eden Thottam]]'' (1980)\n#''[[Muthuchippikal]]'' (1980) .... Sadashivan\n#''[[Aavesham]]'' (1979)\n#''[[Angakkuri]]'' (1979)\n#''[[Agnivyooham]]'' (1979)\n#''[[Kannukal]]'' (1979) .... Kuruppu\n#''[[Madhurikkunna Rathri]]'' (1978)\n#''[[Samayamayilla Polum]]'' (1978)\n#''[[Madhuram Thirumadhuram]]'' (1976) ... vakeel\n#''[[Sindooram]]'' (1976) - Debut film\n#''[[Olavum Theeravum]]'' (1970)\n#''[[Madhuvidhu]]'' (1970)\n#''[[Velutha Kathreena]]'' (1968)\n#''[[Thokkukal Kadha Parayunnu]]'' (1968)\n#''[[Pathirapattu]]'' (1967)(uncredited role)\n#''[[Thalirukal]]'' (1967) (uncredited role)\n#''Ente Kunju'' (unreleased)\n{{div col end}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{IMDb name|0033245|name=Mala Aravindan}}\n* [http://en.msidb.org/displayProfile.php?category=actors&artist=Mala%20Aravindan&limit=233 Mala Aravindan at MSI]\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Aravindan, Mala}}\n[[Category:Indian male film actors]]\n[[Category:Male actors in Malayalam cinema]]\n[[Category:Male actors from Thrissur]]\n[[Category:20th-century Indian male actors]]\n[[Category:1939 births]]\n[[Category:2015 deaths]]